{"tid":1083925,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【遇到難題】蘋果放棄無線充電器AirPower 工程師無法阻止裝置過熱","createTime":"2019-03-30T04:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T09:05:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"717c7e693de3eae8386d23b44e9111394cccb343","tid":1083925,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:18:42.000Z","msg":"1小時前2.5K<br />\n即時國際<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190330/large/1553910714_eb44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190330%2Flarge%2F1553910714_eb44.jpg&h=c6e7dc58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果正式放棄無線充電器AirPower(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n美國蘋果公司兩年前宣佈計劃推出無線充電板「AirPower」，果迷等了又等，卻等到壞消息，蘋果公司正式表示研發「AirPower」失敗，放棄項目，原因是「AirPower」未能達到「高水準」要求。外界猜測，或與技術上無法防止充電板過熱有關。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果表示︰「經過多番努力後，我們認為『AirPower』未能達到我們所要求的高水準，我們要取消此項目。」蘋果硬件工程部門主管里喬(Dan Riccio)向傳媒發電郵指︰「我們向期待它面世的客戶致歉，我們仍相信未來要朝着無線技術方面發展，亦會致力向此方向前進。」<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n「AirPower」的設計原為一板三充，能同時為一部對應無線充電的新iPhone加Apple Watch加AirPods三機同時充電，當時蘋果預計2018年推出市場，並形容其為「世界級無線充電器」。<br />\n<br />\n不過直至上年尾，蘋果公司仍未推出「AirPower」，有熟悉內情的人士格魯伯（Jon Gruber）透露︰「曾經有工程師看過『AirPower』的設計後表示，它不會成功的，熱力問題，現在同一批工程師就擺出『早就說了』的樣子。」<br />\n<br />\n「AirPower」泡湯可能會影響其他的無線產品，如無線耳機「AirPods」，推出「AirPods」時，蘋果在宣傳上指，預計它可以配合無線充電器使用。而市場上蘋果的競爭對手華為和三星則已在更早前已推出無線充電產品。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司<br />\n<br />\n免費訂閱《蘋果動新聞》， 無懼霸權橫行！立即登記！<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.adai.ly/bXz2v29BrV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.adai.ly%2FbXz2v29BrV&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7ZFs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=4a180b30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.adai.ly/bXz2v29BrV</a> <br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n《動腦Q》周末主題夜<br />\n追加星期六、日 9:30 pm<br />\n星期一至五 10:30 pm<br />\nDay Day Q the money!"},{"pid":"8d4c5323c460558b2baef77a774b743fe1ace5d9","tid":1083925,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:20:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190330/59429326\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190330%2F59429326&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7ZFs2tgc95e9lhkBuxw3Ky4%3D&h=89a54c4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190330%2F59429326&h=52ace978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190330/59429326</a>"},{"pid":"dde5d49bcb1cb78f48f351599f27a4820d57ee57","tid":1083925,"uid":36134,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:27:25.000Z","msg":"蘋果呢一兩年有無新技術係見得人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵埋咁多錢 <br />\n結果創新同研發做得仲衰過支為同三星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dda142c6e7e28af50dc5e0ce2a8467b6cabfdf6","tid":1083925,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1880ede3c2bf26ac41296db223c40f77c23aca","tid":1083925,"uid":4525,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"蘋果已死"},{"pid":"023547ab2849008a1112f852a6e3b6aafab8738c","tid":1083925,"uid":231725,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:30:18.000Z","msg":"如果當初Apple Watch 用Qi無線充<br />\n成件事簡單好多"},{"pid":"6b76bc03d941b99d09fc980ace6ebae729004842","tid":1083925,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T04:32:19.000Z","msg":"比個機會 samsung , 華為 去研發, 係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ef388164645761ab61d58980664e7304ccac23","tid":1083925,"uid":49918,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy"